\
**Statement 4:**\
To our allies in the West, the time for words has passed. We need your full and unequivocal support in our fight against this monstrous regime. We need more weapons, more sanctions, and more international pressure to suffocate their war machine. Stand with us, or be damned for your inaction.\
\
**Statement 5:**\
We must expose Russia for the malignant cancer it is. The Kremlin is a cesspool of corruption and brutality, a black hole of human rights abuses and war crimes. They are a pariah state, unworthy of any respect or legitimacy. Those who support or appease them are complicit in their heinous deeds.\
\
**Statement 6:**\
Our hatred for these invaders is righteous and justified. We will not rest until every last Russian soldier is driven from our land, until justice is served for their countless atrocities. Ukraine will rise from this ordeal stronger, more united, and more determined than ever to crush this tyrannical beast.\
